OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ruth Bourne
OL,5,FRuth Bourne, Age: 97, Women's Royal
OL,6,FNaval Service
OL,8,FInterviewed 7 March 2024
OL,10,FWorking at sites around Bletchley Park
OL,11,Fin Buckinghamshire, Mrs Bourne was a
OL,12,FBombe machine operator and checker.
OL,14,FAfter joining the Wrens she was chosen
OL,15,Fto work at the secret site set up to
OL,16,Fdecode intercepted Nazi messages.
OL,18,FBletchley had been compiling
OL,19,Fintelligence for the Allied High
OL,20,FCommand for well over a year before D-
OL,21,FDay.
