OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ruth Bourne
OL,5,F"I am not really sure why it
OL,6,Fhappened," said Mrs Bourne.
OL,8,F"But we went to our training camp as
OL,9,Fnormally we all did and when we were
OL,10,Fall given categories I was put into a
OL,11,Fcategory called SDX special duties.
OL,13,F"There were maybe half a dozen of us
OL,14,Fand we said 'what's that?' And we were
OL,15,Ftold 'We don't know.' That's all we
OL,16,Fwere told."
OL,18,FThe monumental task was to decode
OL,19,Fmessages that had been encrypted via
OL,20,Fthe Enigma cypher device.
