OL,5,FAccording to Bletchley Park's website:
OL,6,F"These devices typically changed
OL,7,Fsettings every 24 hours and with 159
OL,8,Fquintillion possible combinations
OL,9,Fevery day, the staff at Bletchley Park
OL,10,Fworked around the clock to break the
OL,11,Fsettings by hand."
OL,13,FThe Bombes were designed by Alan
OL,14,FTuring and were electro-mechanical
OL,15,Fmachines helping to speed up the
OL,16,Fprocess.
OL,18,FMrs Bourne said: "It had all the
OL,19,Fcomponents of an Enigma machine, the
OL,20,Fdrums, the wheels and the plugs.
