OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ruth Bourne
OL,5,F"It was searching for the reasonable
OL,6,Fpossible answer to any of the paired
OL,7,Fletters of an Enigma machine. There
OL,8,Fwere three banks of wheels replicating
OL,9,Fthe drums on an Enigma machine...we
OL,10,Fput the drums onto rows of rods, being
OL,11,Fextremely accurate.
OL,13,F"Then we went round the back of the
OL,14,Fmachine and were plugging in pairs of
OL,15,Fletters.
OL,17,F"One of the difficulties of breaking
OL,18,FEnigma was the pairs of letters on the
OL,19,FEnigma machine that were very complex.
OL,21,F"Then we set the machine going."
